{"tid":164724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞漢索食物被拒　遭2同鄉木棍皮鞭痛毆","createTime":"2017-03-21T01:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T10:24:50.000Z","uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecee8a5a15d278050a4bec85d71f2b29ae9a9846","tid":164724,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:20:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">南亞漢索食物被拒　遭2同鄉木棍皮鞭痛毆<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/bkn-20170321060740038-0321_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170321%2Fbkn-20170321060740038-0321_00822_001.html&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=25dc02d3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/bkn-20170321060740038-0321_00822_001.html</a></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀又有南亞幫毆傷同鄉案。現場漆咸道南100號，清晨5時許，一名南亞裔男子途經上址，疑向2名男同鄉索取食物，詎料發生爭執，有人以木棍及皮鞭襲擊對方後逃去，事主頭部及左眼受傷，他負傷報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，將受傷事主送院治理，並在附近兜截兇徒蹤影，惜沒有發現，正對案件展開調查。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/21/091948_1cc49416dbb8aa53fc12a9a74a9f1410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F21%2F091948_1cc49416dbb8aa53fc12a9a74a9f1410.jpg&h=eeb572ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170321/photo/bkn-20170321060740038-0321_00822_001_03p.jpg?20170321082041\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170321%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170321060740038-0321_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20170321082041&h=5ebfb160&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81f81ee28f5fd4238935563b6bd5438c761b0aef","tid":164724,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02e6c09d42b0a0df9116cbca5ddafb733f42bcb","tid":164724